  <brief_title>Assessment With CCTA and MRI in Asymptomatic Patients With Type 2 Diabetes for Detection of Unrecognized Myocardial Scar in Subclinical Coronary Atherosclerosis</brief_title>
  <acronym>ACCREDIT</acronym>
  <official_title>Assessment With Cardiac Computed Tomography Angiography (CCTA) and Magnetic Resonance Imaging (MRI) in Asymptomatic Patients With Type 2 Diabetes for Detection of Unrecognized Myocardial Scar in Subclinical Coronary Atherosclerosis</official_title>
