  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is aimed to answer the clinical question of the prevalence of myocardial scar in
      asymptomatic patients with type 2 Diabetes Mellitus with a special focus on the diagnostic
      efficacy of Xenetix® 350-enhanced 64-rows MDCT for the visualisation of the coronary arterial
      tree and secondarily for the assessment of myocardial viability when using Dotarem®
      enhanced-cardioMR as the gold standard examination.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
